summary: This is a pretty cool mod it adds a new giant companion to whiterun.
descriptionHtml:
In this mod you will find a new giant companion in whiterun by big i really mean it. Anyway he carries an even bigger version of the giants club to fit his size. O and beware this guy is a lunatic that attacks anything in his path besides you of coarse anyway enjoy this mod cause i had alot fun with it and hope you like it. 
                                           LOCATION:
You can find jave in whiterun as soon as you walk in you will notice him trust me. Thats it have fun.
author: austin
